1:14|Darby|Hallow a fast, proclaim a solemn assembly, gather the  elders, [and] all the inhabitants of the land to the house of  Jehovah your God, and cry unto Jehovah.
1:14|KJV|Sanctify ye a fast, call a solemn assembly, gather the elders and all the inhabitants of the land into the house of the LORD your God, and cry unto the LORD,
