2:2|Darby|a day of darkness and gloom, a day of clouds and gross  darkness, as the dawn spread upon the mountains; -- a great  people and a strong; there hath not been ever the like, neither  shall be any more after them, to the years of generations and  generations.
2:2|KJV|A day of darkness and of gloominess, a day of clouds and of thick darkness, as the morning spread upon the mountains: a great people and a strong; there hath not been ever the like, neither shall be any more after it, even to the years of many generations.
